            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指升81點報26442點 勝宏登場高開逾57%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓與台灣股市今早先後破頂，港股開市初段亦造好，恒生指數開市報26442點，升81點或0.31%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報5092點，升26點或0.53%；國企指數以8936點開市，升37點或0.42%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股互有升跌，滙控(00005)開報142.2元，暫時無升跌；友邦(01299)開報82.95元，跌0.66%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報138.2元，升0.88%；騰訊(00700)開報523元，升0.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中移動(00941)按中國會計準則的首季歸母淨利按年降4.2%；該股今早開報82元，升0.24%。天齊鋰業(09696)發盈喜，料首季淨利最少增15倍；該股今早開報63.1元，漲8.33%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230703-174831__source-web_00941-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230703-174831__source-web_00941-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">勝宏科技(02476)今早掛牌，在競價時段以330元開市，較招股價209.88元高57.23%。上周五上市的群核科技(00068)悉數行使超額配股權，今早於競價時段開報37元，回吐1.18%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"勝宏科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/300476-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"勝宏科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/300476-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">勝宏科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代(03750)小股東擬減持5800萬股A股詢價後，初步確定每股作價410.34元人幣；該公司H股今早開報712元，升1.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，以折讓價6.07%配股籌15億元的威勝控股(03393)，今早則開報30.9元，跌3.26%；折讓8.35%配股籌5.23億元的和譽(02256)開報13.29元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15898773-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8781%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126442%e9%bb%9e-%e5%8b%9d%e5%ae%8f%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
